    "description": {
      "value": "<em>The need to avenge those you loved drives you to great deeds.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>You must have a close family member or other loved one slain by a specific challenging foe or that foe's minions, or have the Raiders or Vengeance background.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You gain a +1 bonus on saving throws, attack rolls, and weapon damage rolls against your chosen foe and known minions of that foe.<br/><br/><b>Goal</b><br/> Thwart your chosen foe.<br/><br/><b>Completion Benefit</b><br/>You gain a +1 bonus on all saving throws. This bonus stacks with this feats's bonus against your foe and its minions, should they survive.",
